      This build uses 3 pieces of Rey Dau combined with the best-in-slot armor pieces available,
      letting us max out both Agitator and Weakness Exploit.
    </p>

    <p>
      The key feature is high Latent Power levels, giving this set the highest theoretical damage
      output. The downside is that Latent Power can be inconsistent, as it has high up and down
      times. And when the up times overlap with zone transitions, or timings in the fight where you
      can't attack or deal less damage due to monster states, it can lead to damage loss.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you get hit a lot, you actually will have a higher latent power uptime. If this is an
      advantage solely depends on you :)
    </p>

